public class Groupssettings
extends com.google.api.client.googleapis.services.GoogleClient

Service definition for Groupssettings (v1).

Groups Settings Api

For more information about this service, see the API Documentation

This service uses JsonHttpRequestInitializer to initialize global parameters via its Groupssettings.Builder. Sample usage: 

  public class GroupssettingsRequestInitializer implements JsonHttpRequestInitializer {
      public void initialize(JsonHttpRequest request) {
        GroupssettingsRequest groupssettingsRequest = (GroupssettingsRequest)request;
        groupssettingsRequest.setPrettyPrint(true);
        groupssettingsRequest.setKey(ClientCredentials.KEY);
    }
  }
